title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim Update 13 - new build available
description:
In this video we will look at what has been added and what has been fixed in the third beta release for Sim Update 13 which will be released in a few weeks. The list is pretty long and this build contains performance enhancements as well as fixed for several aircrafts and scenery issues reported by users.
